author: Koopsas

text: I had the intention of making this a private video and link it to some people when they ask me to listen to some of my songs, but I figured I might as well make it public. Making music and remixing is just a hobby of mine and lately (mostly in 2010) I haven't been able to do much. The little free time I have is used to play video games. Thankfully, this will be a pretty relaxing summer so I'll start doing some new stuff for fun.
author: SupraDarky
